        "solution_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">স্বচ্ছ = সু+অচ্ছ </span><span class=\"english\">- </span><span class=\"english\">স্বরসন্ধি</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">সু</span><span class=\"english\">বন্ত = </span><span class=\"english\">সু</span><span class=\"english\">প্‌+অন্ত </span><span class=\"english\">- </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যঞ্জনসন্ধি</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">যজ্ঞ = যজ্‌+ন </span><span class=\"english\">- </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যঞ্জনসন্ধি </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">পরিষ্কৃত= পরি+কৃত </span><span class=\"english\">- </span><span class=\"english\">বিশেষ নিয়মে সাধিত ব্যঞ্জনসন্ধি </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">দুগ্ধ= দুহ্‌+ত </span><span class=\"english\">- </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যঞ্জনসন্ধি</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বণ্টন</span><span class=\"english\">:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">প্রতিটি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সন্ধিবিচ্ছেদ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সন্ধির</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নাম</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পাবে</span><span class=\"english\">। (০১</span><span class=\"english\">×</span><span class=\"english\">৫=০৫ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।)</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(</span><span class=\"english\">যেকোনো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ধরনের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বরাদ্দকৃত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কর্তন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে</span><span class=\"english\">।)</span></p><p></p>"
