        "solution_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">ক+</span><span class=\"english\">iv</span><span class=\"english\">; </span><span class=\"english\">খ+</span><span class=\"english\">v</span><span class=\"english\">; গ+ </span><span class=\"english\">i</span><span class=\"english\">; </span><span class=\"english\">ঘ+</span><span class=\"english\">ii</span><span class=\"english\"> ;</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঙ+</span><span class=\"english\">iii</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বণ্টন</span><span class=\"english\">:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">প্রতিটি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মিলক</span><span class=\"english\">রণের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পাবে</span><span class=\"english\">। (০১</span><span class=\"english\">×</span><span class=\"english\">৫=০৫ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।)</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(</span><span class=\"english\">যেকোনো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ধরনের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বরাদ্দকৃত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কর্তন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে</span><span class=\"english\">।)</span></p><p></p>"
